OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start, perhaps a light
OL,6,Fshower or two over Orkney, then
OL,7,Fbrightening up from the north with
OL,8,Fsome sunny spells developing in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Fresh northerly winds,
OL,10,Ffeeling cooler.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will stay dry through the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight. Some prolonged
OL,14,Fspells of evening sunshine leading to
OL,15,Fclear spells overnight. Fresh
OL,16,Fnortherly evening winds will ease and
OL,17,Fback northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
