OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FDry and bright first thing but
OL,6,Fincreasingly clouding over from the
OL,7,Fwest through the morning with a few
OL,8,Foutbreaks of light rain through the
OL,9,Fafternoon and evening, mainly for
OL,10,FOrkney.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fand Wednesday mainly dry and cloudy
OL,14,Fbut with some sunny intervals, most
OL,15,Flikely for Shetland. Generally
OL,16,Fcloudier on Tuesday with some patchy
OL,17,Fdrizzle.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
